SECTION 7: Hypotheses
1. Low purchase frequency increases churn risk  
2. Higher inactivity (recency) leads to churn  
3. More support tickets indicate dissatisfaction → churn  
4. Low engagement users churn more  
5. Campaign exposure reduces churn
